{"tid":2044179,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（溫故知新）美國制裁重創俄羅斯富豪 財富總額一天縮水160 億美元","createTime":"2020-05-31T02:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T03:53:10.000Z","uid":50457,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"623588c69668b13946a8380ba2a8c316a89423f9","tid":2044179,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"上周五美國發布了新一輪對俄羅斯的制裁決定，包括多名俄羅斯高官、富豪以及國防出口公司在內的38個個人及實體「上榜」。這被認為是川普政府迄今對俄羅斯採取的最嚴厲的一次制裁措施，美國高級官員形容，制裁對象多是普京「核心圈子」成員。<br />\n<br />\n2<br />\n針對美國的動作，俄羅斯外交部發表聲明回應稱「對這次制裁及以後的新制裁，俄方都會予以強硬回擊。」聲明稱，美國以制裁手段清除海外市場的競爭對手，實際把自己變成市場經濟和自由公平競爭的敵人。<br />\n<br />\n3<br />\n受此影響，俄羅斯遭遇股匯雙殺，該國股指暴跌逾11%，盧布一度跌破60關口，創2016年6月以來最大跌幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/finance/8llg834.amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Ffinance%2F8llg834.amp&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdG5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=3956b367\" target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/finance/8llg834.amp</a><br />\n<br />\n美國制裁唔係打咀炮，出大絕就算富豪都重傷"},{"pid":"3a68b77947c53edfee668be74580fc33719f2451","tid":2044179,"uid":345989,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:05:37.000Z","msg":"美國而家開地圖炮<br />\n全部都要死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf61ba59c9b06d2cb1d7c17a3732c93a9f88c867","tid":2044179,"uid":124859,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ea3f82e54ff9f623278ef723dbab223ce7b4af4","tid":2044179,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"真‧地圖炮"},{"pid":"d5ea0a685eca2f06790a032a5a28f6e665bbeef4","tid":2044179,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdG5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=4cf026b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc</a><br />\n係貼就貼d真正媒體source啦認真"},{"pid":"129dceac108a6356d7a0277372dc3e5c54b55b15","tid":2044179,"uid":34230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:15:09.000Z","msg":"咪post content farm啦屌"},{"pid":"5518dfdc22e4f6f50922a529b4244b72ee09ead7","tid":2044179,"uid":44718,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:25:41.000Z","msg":"共狗: 我制裁自己啲富豪嗰陣佢地一秒無晒啲錢啦, 一日少160億咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ba03fe7864392bd2c7a7444e261a021d490e68","tid":2044179,"uid":91721,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d5ea0a685eca2f06790a032a5a28f6e665bbeef4","tid":2044179,"uid":10014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:12:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://kknews.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdG5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=4cf026b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc</a><br />\n係貼就貼d真正媒體source啦認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:37:03.000Z","msg":"kknews<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全亞洲最大content farm"},{"pid":"e4254f02b116bf10c5dc565fccd8bf44b5befe5f","tid":2044179,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:49:44.000Z","msg":"彭博商業周刊 / 中文版 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bbwhk/posts/1019032764910371/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbbwhk%2Fposts%2F1019032764910371%2F&d=zeAGpz59Z2vRp%2Fz3xPaAdG5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=6c1e094e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bbwhk/posts/1019032764910371/</a><br />\n2018年4月10日 &middot; 公開<br />\n【即時頭條】美國制裁重創俄羅斯富豪 一天縮水160億美元<br />\n對於俄羅斯富豪來說，這一天真是太痛苦了。<br />\n在美國近期宣佈實施制裁之後，俄羅斯富豪們的綜合資產淨值在4月9日損失160億美元，過去一年取得的增長完全泡湯。<br />\n在彭博億萬富豪指數上榜的27位俄羅斯大亨中，有26人身家縮水。首當其衝的是西伯利亞鎳業大亨Vladimir Potanin，其財富損失22.5億美元。盧克石油行政總裁Vagit Alekperov財富減少13.7億美元，Renova Group的Viktor Vekselberg損失了12.8億美元。<br />\n特朗普政府近期宣佈實施制裁，報復俄羅斯干涉2016美國大選，Vekselberg即是受制裁的7位俄羅斯大亨之一。他4月9日採取措施以限制美國製裁對其瑞士控股公司的影響。<br />\n同在被制裁之列的Oleg Deripaska 4月9日損失9.05億美元，其財富在過去兩個交易日裡減少超過20億美元。他的損失源於他的工業集團En+ Group Plc，根據倫敦股票交易所的資料，該股股價自4月5日以來暴跌了54%。通過En+，Deripaska擁有俄鋁一半股權，而這家鋁業巨頭也是制裁物件。<br />\nMOEX俄羅斯指數4月9日下跌8.3%，為四年來最大跌幅。盧布兌美元匯率下跌3.7%至60.3盧布。撰文/彭博社<br />\n#俄羅斯富豪受重創"},{"pid":"9331d623df3bffa8c1d2f3c669284c40666fe660","tid":2044179,"uid":59929,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:52:23.000Z","msg":"佢地唔明世界商業秩序係邊個揸旗<br />\n係都要頭破血流先識驚"},{"pid":"48ca1ad90d9894f8300b5f9d22c6a4b53b3e58fd","tid":2044179,"uid":343754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T03:53:10.000Z","msg":"所以咪話攬炒要死都係死窮撚先<br />\n未同人攬炒先自炒"}]}